evidence: CT provides excellent structural detail and shows calcification and bone.
PET or SPECT provides metabolic and molecular insights

triples.evidence: CT has already been combined with PET or SPECT, and MRI has also been paired with PET in what we call PET/MRI scanners - Siemens, for example, developed a system called the MRI Pattern Scanner to take advantage of this synergy.
